[Made in collaboration with Sedivalle!](https://cults3d.com/en/users/Sedivalle/3d-models)
Thumbnail painted by the excellent Draconian Minipainting!

This pack contains Regular, Heavy Weapons, and Command versions of Sedivalle's Exterminators, resculpted and adjusted for printing at 8mm scale for all of your mass wargames, or scaled up as you see fit!

Options include:
***Small Arms:***
Fist, Claw and Dual Claws. 5x Poses each.

***Command:***
Champion
Banner Bearer with Fist or Bolter
Captain with choice of large or small crest

***Heavy Weapons:***
Heavy Bolters, Plasma, Heat Rays, or Disintegrator cannons.
5x Poses each. Mirroring suggested for additional variety.

If you'd like to keep up with my current projects, and support the modelling work I do, please check out my patreon at: www.patreon.com/Daffmakes

Also, check out my new discord to chat with other enjoyers of my work and post your own stuff! www.discord.gg/JuJBmc6mQs

Provides a version of Woddish's excellent Tiny Tank Fancy APC and related things that have been sliced into major parts that are enabled to be quickly swapped and edited for customization by changing visibility of components between different options for hatches, side doors, symbols/icons, and crew. The eventual end game would be the ability to build any Mars based Monoceros chassis vehicle with this tool.

This is intended for designers and modelers to product their own faction customized vehicles from in a standardized and high quality form.

If you like what I did and want to leave a tip it would be appreciated.
https://paypal.me/jimmyzimms

Leverages Orcstain's excellent astartes symbols and bolter from Lord Chronos. Crew figure based on a DangItBlobby jarhead

New part contributions are welcome!
